OL,3,CDriving medical standards are set to
OL,4,Cchange in Jersey
OL,6,FDrivers of minibuses, coaches and
OL,7,Flarger vans in Jersey may need a
OL,8,Fmedical certificate to prove they are
OL,9,Ffit enough to drive from October.
OL,11,FThe government has confirmed that the
OL,12,Fmedical standards needed for driving
OL,13,Fare being updated to bring the island
OL,14,Fcloser to EU and UK law.
OL,16,FThe changes will come into force on 5
OL,17,FOctober 2024.
