OL,3,CDriving medical standards are set to
OL,4,Cchange in Jersey
OL,6,FAnyone applying or renewing a 'Group 2
OL,7,Flicence' will need to submit a
OL,8,Fcertificate proving they have not had
OL,9,Fa seizure or taken prescribed
OL,10,Fmedication to treat epilepsy in the
OL,11,Flast five years, and that they have
OL,12,Fnot had two or more seizures in the
OL,13,Flast 10 years.
OL,15,FDrivers must also have had a medical
OL,16,Fexamination by a specialist in
OL,17,Fneurology who deems they are healthy
OL,18,Fenough to drive.
